text: Tetyana Budko (ukr. Тетяна Будко; born 16 May 1984ВК ЗГИА) is a Ukrainian volleyball player. She played at the 2003 Women's European Volleyball Championship, 2002/2003 European Cups, 2004/2005 European Championships, and 2003 FIVB Women's U20 World Championship. == References == == Other websites == * http://www.bvbinfo.com/player.asp?ID=5303 Category:1984 births Category:Ukrainian volleyball players Category:Living people
